text:
Mrs Crunch ‘I forgot I had a baby’ Mum goes into a coma and suffers AMNESIA after bad reaction to epidural – and didn’t believe people when told she’d given birth 
For Bernadette Strange, 35, the memories of the moment her son Elijah entered the world are just not there By NATALIE KEEGAN
